@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_AUTH_TOKEN_HERE

### Chat with Bot (Starting a new conversation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "Hello, can you tell me about the available courses?"
}

### Chat with Bot (Continuing a conversation with history)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": "What level are they for?",
    "history": [
        { "role": "user", "content": "Hello, can you tell me about the available courses?" },
        { "role": "assistant", "content": "We have various courses in Web Development, Data Science, and Mobile App Development." }
    ]
}

### Test Chatbot without message (Error case)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/chatbot/chat
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "message": ""
}
